! Input file for fitting with WAVE
!
! -1 !Iterative parabolic minimization for one parameter between the boundaries
1 !Number of parameters to optimize via Monte-Carlo minimization
!
"URSHIFT(1)" 14. 20. ! variable and boundaries or start and step size resp.
!
!
0.00001 ! tolerance for conversion
10 ! max. number of iteration
"python3 wave_adjust.py" ! command called by WAVE to calculate chi2 and write it to wave_adjust.dat
